OL,3,CScots Euros fan says blood is '100%
OL,4,CGerman' after lifesaving transplant
OL,6,FA Scotland fan travelling to Munich to
OL,7,Fwatch his team play in the first game
OL,8,Fof the Euros has told how his life was
OL,9,Fsaved by a bone marrow transplant from
OL,10,Fa German donor almost 25 years ago.
OL,12,FAlly Brown, 41, who lives in
OL,13,FHaddington, East Lothian, was given a
OL,14,Fbone marrow transplant aged 16.
OL,16,FPrior to that, he had four years of
OL,17,Ftreatment for acute lymphoblastic
OL,18,Fleukaemia ` a type of blood cancer `
OL,19,Fwhich had reoccurred three times.
