OL,3,CScots Euros fan says blood is '100%
OL,4,CGerman' after lifesaving transplant
OL,6,FHe said: "I'll be cheering on
OL,7,FScotland, but my blood is my German
OL,8,Fdonor's blood."
OL,10,FScotland will take on Germany in their
OL,11,Ffirst game of the 2024 Euros on Friday.
OL,13,FMr Brown said: "It's dead exciting we
OL,14,Fare playing against Germany in the
OL,15,Ftournament opener and I'm so lucky to
OL,16,Fhave a ticket, I can't wait.
OL,18,F"My blood is 100% German so the
OL,19,Fcountry will always be close to my
OL,20,Fheart. But I'll be shouting and
OL,21,Fsinging for Scotland on Friday night."
