OL,3,CScots Euros fan says blood is '100%
OL,4,CGerman' after lifesaving transplant
OL,6,FMr Brown received a bone marrow
OL,7,Ftransplant from a German woman through
OL,8,Fstem cell charity Anthony Nolan, which
OL,9,Fwas founded in 1974.
OL,11,FIt matches donors and patients and was
OL,12,Fset up by Shirley Nolan to find a
OL,13,Fmatch for her son, Anthony, who had a
OL,14,Frare blood disorder.
OL,16,FWhile a match was not found for
OL,17,FAnthony, who died in 1979 aged seven,
OL,18,Fthe charity has since facilitated more
OL,19,Fthan 26,500 transplants for people
OL,20,Faround the world.
