OL,3,CScots Euros fan says blood is '100%
OL,4,CGerman' after lifesaving transplant
OL,6,FSpeaking about his donor, Mr Brown
OL,7,Fsaid they keep in touch on Facebook
OL,8,Fand use Google Translate to
OL,9,Fcommunicate.
OL,11,F"My donor has given me the most
OL,12,Fwonderful gift. She's given me 24 more
OL,13,Fyears of life and counting, and I am
OL,14,Fso grateful," he added.
OL,16,F"We have swapped pictures, and my
OL,17,Fpartner sent her a message to say
OL,18,Fthanks, too. Saving a life isn't just
OL,19,Fa gift for that one person, it's for
OL,20,Ftheir family and friends too.
