OL,3,CScots Euros fan says blood is '100%
OL,4,CGerman' after lifesaving transplant
OL,6,F"That's why it's so important that
OL,7,Feveryone who can donate is registered
OL,8,Fwith Anthony Nolan so that other
OL,9,Fpeople's lives can be saved, like mine
OL,10,Fwas."
OL,12,FHenny Braund, chief executive of
OL,13,FAnthony Nolan, said: "It's wonderful
OL,14,Fto see Ally going to cheer Scotland on
OL,15,Fin Germany, the home of his lifesaving
OL,16,Fdonor.
