OL,3,CScots Euros fan says blood is '100%
OL,4,CGerman' after lifesaving transplant
OL,6,F"Sadly, someone in the UK is diagnosed
OL,7,Fwith blood cancer every 13 minutes and
OL,8,Ffor people with blood cancer or a
OL,9,Fblood disorder, a stem cell transplant
OL,10,Fcan be their last chance of survival.
OL,12,F"As the Euros are kicking off, we're
OL,13,Fcalling on football fans aged 16-30 to
OL,14,Fjoin our One Million United campaign
OL,15,Fby joining the stem cell register.
OL,17,F"Just a quick swab is all it takes to
OL,18,Fjoin our team of potential lifesavers
OL,19,Fand you could end up giving someone
OL,20,Flike Ally a second chance of life."
